"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-29-What-makes-the-2024-Paris-Summer-Olympics-special--1vDjLykDxD2-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  With the Summer Olympics back in the French capital after 100 years, Sideline Story asks what makes Paris 2024 different from previous editions of the Games? Also in this episode, we discuss our expectations for the performances of Chinese athletes in France, as well as our personal predictions for the highlights of this year's Olympics. In addition, we touch on how the new, trendy sports among Generation Z have changed the dynamics of the Games.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"